{"tid":1791650,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"靈異現象：平時幾唔信黑警講野都好，黑警話手足屋企有軍火，就即刻信，唔信就係割席。","createTime":"2019-12-21T04:26:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-21T08:47:28.000Z","uid":33904,"like":123,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"622e02b87055e587231d81a4b5cc5c36455070c1","tid":1791650,"uid":33904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:26:33.000Z","msg":"呢d係咪弱智黎？<br />\n懷疑黑警=割席<br />\n信黑警=核爆都唔割<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n乜鳩破窗，英雄化被捕人，<br />\n如果有日無lala比黑警上門擺低幾枝槍，<br />\n然後成個連登都叫自己英雄，不割席，信哂黑警個套，有人想幫我查，反而比人屌割席，都唔知笑好定喊好。"},{"pid":"70dfa90f5297e44fba34274000354a0cf0bd21d3","tid":1791650,"uid":112081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:27:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"47e6df2ad110f1ca95b2cf4d15f930cc2f60d2d5","tid":1791650,"uid":33418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43ff428f7a5cb58a3778be84a1c4f4714b6d2772","tid":1791650,"uid":231583,"like":25,"dislike":1,"score":24,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:28:19.000Z","msg":"有班心理學家覺得唔爭住認=前線手足會傷心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21f75173915823e8f3e8ff99018533db3754fd33","tid":1791650,"uid":273218,"like":3,"dislike":15,"score":-12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:31:41.000Z","msg":"你呢d咪分化同散步謠言囉<br />\n<br />\n舊12月條友比人周過係事實<br />\n事實係當時未有反送中<br />\n咁點可以講成係手足<br />\n你唔好話陳同佳係手足?<br />\n比黑警拉就係手足?<br />\n係咪要驗腦<br />\n雖然條靚仔好可能被黑警老屈<br />\n但唔係手足講咩割唔割"},{"pid":"cb2ff0c00d937cdbeae51520443978b77a26616f","tid":1791650,"uid":3457,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-12-21T04:34:39.000Z","msg":"其實一直有人想亂咁認曬d柒野<br />\n明明成件事仲未清就搶住認<br />\n唔認就係當前線Condom <br />\n佢係味前線手足都唔撚知就唔好撚亂講野喇"},{"pid":"3203dd3a18630433632813b82883b682e6786914","tid":1791650,"uid":92453